dict.string: Rigid armor of metal plates and the heaviest animal hides

This type of armor mimics older, more archaic plate armor. It is made from a hardened composite shell. It relatively lightweight, and is efficient both at energy dispersal and projectile deflection. It is designed soecifically to foil energy weapons. These armors are the only type designed specifically to be used with armor add-ons.

Powered armor can be handled in different ways, depending on the size of the armor. If the armor is relatively light, than simply treat as a normal aror. Heavy mechanical suits are beyond the scope of this work.
